{"tid":1165784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又亮劍】中國駐美大使崔天凱：談判大門仍然敞開　北京準備好繼續與華府貿易談判","createTime":"2019-05-22T04:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T05:15:16.000Z","uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"125ecc9ed971d435122551aa74a967732f8ff2c7","tid":1165784,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰升級之際，中國駐美大使崔天凱周二表示，北京當局已準備好與華府繼續就貿易進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n崔天凱接受霍士新聞頻道訪問時說：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國仍舊準備好持續與我們同僚進行談判以達成協議。我方大門依舊敞開。</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n美中本月10日舉行貿易談判前，美國總統特朗普突然宣佈調高2,000億美元（1.56萬億港元）進口中國貨的關稅稅率，那次談判亦在無達成協議下結束，之後雙方未再安排高級談判代表進一步磋商。<br />\n<br />\n美國指中國出爾反爾，但崔天凱反指是美國談判代表對過往一年的承諾反悔，並經常改變主意。"},{"pid":"d7a72350ebe03d3543aaa20e27b2709bd6932576","tid":1165784,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190522/59627461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627461&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=70c7b9dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627461&h=869e94ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190522/59627461</a>"},{"pid":"5513749bbd618c9517e6bf9ea53f032237014daa","tid":1165784,"uid":31186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"講到好似美國求你傾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa39b6d7b7adf3289b09e77f1da7fc6dad5262b","tid":1165784,"uid":18955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"「但崔天凱反指是美國談判代表對過往一年的承諾反悔，並經常改變主意。」<br />\n<br />\n咁點解仲要傾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a91082e46e8c09faeb8